title.en: Euro area current account – by main counterparties

definition.en: Current account balance (credits minus debits, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Current account credits (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).
Current account debits (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

Current account balance as a percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (credits minus debits, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working-day adjusted; BPM6 and ESA 2010 standards).

Current account credits as a percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working-day adjusted; BPM6 and ESA 2010 standards).
